{"id": "9228", "revid": "3234315", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=9228", "title": "Fake Dragon Eggs (Phaere's)", "text": "Phaere's Fake Dragon Eggs are an item needed in &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20II%20Chapter%205\"&gt;chapter 5&lt;/a&gt; of and . &lt;a href=\"Phaere\"&gt;Phaere&lt;/a&gt; gives you these eggs to switch them with the real &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Eggs\"&gt;Dragon Eggs&lt;/a&gt; which the &lt;a href=\"Matron%20Mother%20Ardulace\"&gt;Matron Mother Ardulace&lt;/a&gt; plans to sacrifice\nWith these, Matron Mother Ardulace's attempt to summon the &lt;a href=\"Lesser%20Demon%20Lord\"&gt;Lesser Demon Lord&lt;/a&gt; will backfire. Phaere's ritual will succeed, and she will reap the rewards herself, if she sacrifices the real eggs. Alternatively if &lt;a href=\"Solaufein\"&gt;Solaufein&lt;/a&gt; is spared, he can provide &lt;a href=\"Fake%20Dragon%20Eggs%20%28Solaufein%27s%29\"&gt;his own fake eggs&lt;/a&gt;. If this second set of fake eggs is given to her, her ritual will also backfire and you can return the real dragon eggs to &lt;a href=\"Adalon\"&gt;Adalon&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "30425", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=30425", "title": "Fake Dragon Eggs (Solaufein's)", "text": "These Fake Dragon Eggs are given to you by &lt;a href=\"Solaufein\"&gt;Solaufein&lt;/a&gt; if &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; spared him in &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20II%20Chapter%205\"&gt;chapter 5&lt;/a&gt; of and . Solaufein gives you these eggs to switch them with the real &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Eggs\"&gt;Dragon Eggs&lt;/a&gt; which &lt;a href=\"Phaere\"&gt;Phaere&lt;/a&gt; plans to sacrifice.\nWith these, &lt;a href=\"Matron%20Mother%20Ardulace\"&gt;Matron Mother Ardulace&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Phaere\"&gt;Phaere&lt;/a&gt;'s attempts to summon the &lt;a href=\"Lesser%20Demon%20Lord\"&gt;Lesser Demon Lord&lt;/a&gt; will backfire if you give them &lt;a href=\"Fake%20Dragon%20Eggs%20%28Phaere%27s%29\"&gt;Phaere's fake eggs&lt;/a&gt; and these eggs, respectively. These eggs are useful in deceiving &lt;a href=\"Phaere\"&gt;Phaere&lt;/a&gt;, escaping &lt;a href=\"Ust%20Natha\"&gt;Ust Natha&lt;/a&gt; without combat and returning the real &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Eggs\"&gt;Dragon Eggs&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=\"Adalon\"&gt;Adalon&lt;/a&gt;.\nThis is an optional plot element available as part of the &lt;a href=\"The%20Drow%20Summoning%20Ritual\"&gt;The Drow Summoning Ritual&lt;/a&gt; questline."}
