r other , &lt;a href=\"pickpocket\"&gt;pickpocket&lt;/a&gt;ing, &lt;a href=\"Stealth\"&gt;hiding in shadows&lt;/a&gt; and casting of &lt;a href=\"wizard%20spells\"&gt;wizard spells&lt;/a&gt; are not possible while wearing the armor. It also cannot be equipped with other protective &lt;a href=\"item\"&gt;item&lt;/a&gt;s, such as rings of protection.\nWhile the &lt;a href=\"armor\"&gt;armor&lt;/a&gt; does not need any &lt;a href=\"lore\"&gt;lore&lt;/a&gt; in the original \"Baldur's Gate II\" to &lt;a href=\"identify\"&gt;identify&lt;/a&gt; it, a knowledge level of 40 is required in the other . It's worth throughout the &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20series\"&gt;series&lt;/a&gt;.\nLocations.\nUnused references.\nThere are further references to this plate mail in various game files that, however, make no appearance in the or aren't referenced themselves."}
