{"id": "3792", "revid": "278991", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3792", "title": "Manual of Gainful Exercise", "text": "This item appears in &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20%28game%29\"&gt;Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt; and .\nManuals of Gainful Exercise are magical tomes which increase &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; by one point (up to a maximum of 25) and are consumed when the point is added. It can be used by all classes. It has a weight of 25 lbs.\nIf used on a character with a Strength value of 18 (with or without exceptional Strength), this item will skip the (remaining) percentage variants of Str 18 and instead boost the character's Strength to 19.\nIf used on a character with a Strength value of 17 it will be increased to base 18 without any exceptional value, even if the character in question is in the warrior group type."}
