{"id": "9172", "revid": "3234315", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=9172", "title": "Maralee", "text": "Maralee is a &lt;a href=\"chaotic%20good\"&gt;chaotic good&lt;/a&gt; widowed mother and an inhabitant of the werewolf village that's located on the &lt;a href=\"Isle%20of%20Balduran%20South\"&gt;southern half&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=\"Isle%20of%20Balduran\"&gt;Isle of Balduran&lt;/a&gt; in .\nShe waits near the firepit in the village center and will first refer &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; to her &lt;a href=\"Kaishas%20Gan\"&gt;headwoman&lt;/a&gt; before speaking of her own problem.\nDialogue.\n\"Hello, good people. I am Maralee. I have heard that you will fight the wolves in the old ship. Is it true?\"\n\"Please help me, stranger, I have no one left to turn to.\"\n\"My baby, they have him! You must save him! Oh, please!\"\n\"It has been so hard not knowing. Two moons ago my husband took my son out hunting with him. They were attacked by those horrible wolf-creatures. They... they killed my husband and took my baby. Kaishas says that they took the baby away to eat him, but I know he's still alive.\"\n\"They won't go and look for him and they stop me from leaving the village. You have to help me!\"\n\"He's a beautiful little boy with dark hair like his father. He is three moons old and his name is Peladan. They took him from my husband northeast of the village, in the woods.\"\n\"Thank you friends! Please bring him back to me.\""}
{"id": "13416", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=13416", "title": "Maralee's Child", "text": "Maralee's Child is a side quest during &lt;a href=\"Balduran%27s%20Final%20Voyage\"&gt;Balduran's Final Voyage&lt;/a&gt;, one of the quest arches in the expansion.\n&lt;onlyinclude&gt;Maralee is looking for her child. Her husband took her son out for hunting two moons ago and were attacked. The village chieftain is convinced they've eaten her son, but she is convinced he's still alive.&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;\nWalk-through.\nTalk to Maralee right outside the &lt;a href=\"Werewolf%20Village%20Huts%23AR2002\"&gt;Chieftain's House&lt;/a&gt;, once you've talked to the headwoman &lt;a href=\"Kaishas%20Gan\"&gt;Kaishas Gan&lt;/a&gt;. As with other NPC's in this area, she'll tell you to visit Kaishas if you haven't done so yet.\nAgree to help her:\nOr brush her off:\nMaralee's infant son, &lt;a href=\"Peladan\"&gt;Peladan&lt;/a&gt;, is held captive by &lt;a href=\"Karoug\"&gt;Karoug&lt;/a&gt; on the fourth level of the &lt;a href=\"Wandering%20Eye\"&gt;Wandering Eye&lt;/a&gt;. Travel to the &lt;a href=\"Isle%20of%20Balduran%20North\"&gt;north side&lt;/a&gt; of the island, towards the shipwreck. There are other tasks to accomplish in this area, but ultimately you need to save &lt;a href=\"Peladan%20%28item%29\"&gt;the child&lt;/a&gt; from Karoug's clutches and return him to Maralee for your reward."}
