{"id": "24612", "revid": "3234315", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=24612", "title": "Mastering Melee &amp; Magic (Baldur's Gate)", "text": "Baldur's Gate: Enhanced Edition Mastering Melee &amp; Magic is the outdated &lt;a href=\"Game%20guides\"&gt;manual&lt;/a&gt; and rulebook for &lt;a href=\"Beamdog\"&gt;Beamdog&lt;/a&gt;'s \".\nAs part of the \" release, it was replaced by the updated \"&lt;a href=\"Adventurer%27s%20Guide\"&gt;Adventurer's Guide&lt;/a&gt;\". It is still publicly available from &lt;a href=\"https%3A//www.beamdog.com/\"&gt;Beamdog's official website.&lt;/a&gt;"}
