{"id": "13471", "revid": "3234315", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=13471", "title": "Mazzy has challenged Gorf the Squisher", "text": "Mazzy has challenged Gorf the Squisher is a &lt;a href=\"Companions\"&gt;Companion&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Quests\"&gt;Quest&lt;/a&gt; during the \"\" campaign.\nAcquisition.\nThe quest is obtained by bringing &lt;a href=\"Mazzy%20Fentan\"&gt;Mazzy Fentan&lt;/a&gt; into the vicinity of the side door (left of the front door) outside of the &lt;a href=\"Copper%20Coronet\"&gt;Copper Coronet&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Slums%20District\"&gt;Slums District&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Athkatla\"&gt;Athkatla&lt;/a&gt; where an &lt;a href=\"Ogre\"&gt;Ogre&lt;/a&gt; named &lt;a href=\"Gorf%20the%20Squisher\"&gt;Gorf the Squisher&lt;/a&gt; stands (only between the hours 3 and 15).\n\"\"What this? Baby paladin? Girl play dress-up like big warrior? I talk you, pipsqueak. Go home to dolls, this big Gorf's world. I show you difference in wimpy halfling punch and Gorf squishy hit. Watch me.\"\n\"See difference, little nothing? Tiny gives Gorf hurt head. Gorf no like. Gorf will squishy you kind.\"\n\"I can stand by and take your insults to myself but now you have struck an innocent merely to dishonor me. I demand satisfaction, brutish fool!\"\"\nWalkthrough.\nMazzy will challenge him to a duel in the Copper Coronet's fighting pits.\nInside the Copper Coronet, &lt;a href=\"Bunkin\"&gt;Bunkin&lt;/a&gt; can be approached and asked to fetch Gorf for the fight. Doing so, will send the two directly into the fighting pit. However if anyone goes pass Bunkin, northwards towards the stairs, Festule takes an interest and starts a dialog.\nNext to the stairs of the common room, &lt;a href=\"Festule%20the%20Alchemist\"&gt;Festule the Alchemist&lt;/a&gt; will sell &lt;a href=\"Festule%20the%20Alchemist%27s%20Potion\"&gt;a potion&lt;/a&gt; to the group for ( with bargaining) to drug Gorf. It may not be necessary to beat Gorf, but it will grant extra experience.\nReturn with the potion to Bunkin. With a bit of flattery, Bunkin can be persuaded to give the potion to Gorf. Completing this optional step will grant an additional to the party.\nOnce Gorf and Mazzy are ready they both will be teleported to the small fighting pit.Mazzy will be stripped of her equipment and given a &lt;a href=\"Short%20Sword\"&gt;short sword&lt;/a&gt; and a &lt;a href=\"Small%20Shield\"&gt;small shield&lt;/a&gt;. Initially, the sword and shield will NOT be equipped, but will only be in her inventory. You may pause the game to equip her new gear. Also, you may pass gear to her from outside the pit if the character is not too far away. Gorf is only equipped with a regular &lt;a href=\"club\"&gt;club&lt;/a&gt;, and does not drop anything else.\nKilling Gorf is worth , which also completes the quest, granting the party .\nMod content.\nthe &lt;a href=\"Sword%20Coast%20Stratagems\"&gt;Sword Coast Stratagems&lt;/a&gt; mod revised Gorf the squisher, and fixes a coding error."}
