{"id": "3145", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3145", "title": "Medium Shield +1", "text": "Medium Shield +1 is a magical shield which offers a 2 point bonus to &lt;a href=\"Armor%20Class\"&gt;Armor Class&lt;/a&gt;, versus the 1 AC bonus for a standard Medium Shield. It has no penalties or bonuses to AC from specific types of attacks, and weighs 6 lbs. In Baldur's Gate II, like all shields, its appearance has been drastically altered from its counterpart in the original game."}
