{"id": "5947", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5947", "title": "Merchants' League", "text": "The Merchants' League is an organization based in &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20%28city%29\"&gt;Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt; that traded goods and promoted safety among the caravan routes throughout the region surrounding the city. Under the leadership of &lt;a href=\"Dabron%20Sashenstar\"&gt;Dabron Sashenstar&lt;/a&gt; and with the backing of the Dukes of Baldur's Gate, the Merchants' League began to challenge the &lt;a href=\"Iron%20Throne\"&gt;Iron Throne&lt;/a&gt; for the weapons trade in western &lt;a href=\"Faer%C3%BBn\"&gt;Faer\u00fbn&lt;/a&gt;.\nBaldur's Gate.\nIf &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; and party aided &lt;a href=\"Aldeth%20Sashenstar\"&gt;Aldeth Sashenstar&lt;/a&gt; in the first &lt;a href=\"Cloakwood%20Druids\"&gt;Cloakwood area&lt;/a&gt;, Aldeth will be found outside the &lt;a href=\"Merchants%27%20League%20Estate\"&gt;Merchants' League Estate&lt;/a&gt; and will ask you to investigate the company. You eventually realize that the organization has been infiltrated by &lt;a href=\"doppelganger\"&gt;doppelganger&lt;/a&gt;s. You need to kill all the doppelgangers before returning to Aldeth for your reward."}
