{"id": "4873", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4873", "title": "Mirror Image", "text": "The Mirror Image spell allows the wizard to create a number of illusory duplicates of himself which disappear when the wizard is struck by a melee or missile attack. \nWhere to obtain its scroll.\nOther availability.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Ring%20of%20Duplication\"&gt;Ring of Duplication&lt;/a&gt;, only available in , allows the wearer to apply Mirror Image (5 images) thrice per day.\n&lt;a href=\"Monk\"&gt;Dark Moon Monks&lt;/a&gt; get Mirror Image as innate ability at level 11.\nMod content.\n&lt;a href=\"Spell%20Revisions\"&gt;Spell Revisions&lt;/a&gt; mod has changed this arcane spell, revising duration. See below for description:\nMirror Image\nLevel: 2\nSchool: Illusion\nRange: Personal\nDuration: 5 turns\nCasting Time: 2\nArea of Effect: Caster\nSaving Throw: None\nWhen a Mirror Image spell is invoked, the spellcaster causes a number of illusory duplicates of himself to come into being around him. The spell creates two images plus one for every 3 levels of the caster (up to a maximum of eight images at 18th level). These images do exactly what the wizard does, and since the spell causes a blurring and slight distortion when it is cast, it is impossible for opponents to be certain which are the illusions, and which is the actual wizard. When an image is directly struck by a melee or missile attack, magical or otherwise, it disappears, while other existing images remain intact. It is important to note that this will not protect the caster against all attacks, as it is possible for an enemy to choose the real caster amongst all the images. This spell cannot be cast on anyone who is under the effects of a Reflected Image spell, and casting the spell multiple times will not multiply the number of images created."}
{"id": "55937", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=55937", "title": "Mirror Image (SPIN697)", "text": "Mirror Image (SPIN697) is an innate ability available to various creatures. The ability is initiated via script by the AI. \nEffects.\nThe effect is directed at the caster only. \nThe magic behaves as a typical Wizard's &lt;a href=\"Mirror%20Image\"&gt;Mirror Image&lt;/a&gt; arcane spell, although it lasts only 6 rounds and produces 4 images.\nThe innate spell is &lt;a href=\"Power%20level\"&gt;Power level&lt;/a&gt; 2 and can be dispelled."}
