{"id": "6182", "revid": "35448340", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6182", "title": "Hindo's Doom", "text": "Hindo's Doom +3 is an enchanted katana. It has +3 bonus to &lt;a href=\"THAC0\"&gt;THAC0&lt;/a&gt;, it inflicts 1d10+3 points of damage, weighs 3 lbs. and it has a speed factor of 1. The blade can be used once per day to cast the spell &lt;a href=\"Lesser%20Restoration\"&gt;Lesser Restoration&lt;/a&gt;, which removes the effect of &lt;a href=\"Level%20drain\"&gt;Level drain&lt;/a&gt; from a character. This item appears in and in . The weapon can be found in &lt;a href=\"Watcher%27s%20Keep%20%28dungeon%29\"&gt;Watcher's Keep&lt;/a&gt;. It will be dropped by a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20%28Watchers%20Keep%20Final%20Seal%29\"&gt;Dragon&lt;/a&gt; on the fifth level. The weapon can be upgraded by &lt;a href=\"Cespenar\"&gt;Cespenar&lt;/a&gt;, which requires some gold and &lt;a href=\"Hindo%27s%20Hand\"&gt;Hindo's Hand&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nLegend.\nb = Before the upgrade.\na = After the upgrade.\nUpgraded version.\nHindo's Doom +4 now has +4 bonus to damage and THAC0 and the weight has been reduced to 2 lbs. Instead of casting Lesser Restoration once per day, you can now cast &lt;a href=\"Greater%20Restoration\"&gt;Greater Restoration&lt;/a&gt;, it gives the wearer 10% magical resistance and grants complete &lt;a href=\"Death%20Ward\"&gt;immunity against all forms of death magic&lt;/a&gt;."}
