{"id": "6879", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6879", "title": "Psion's Blade", "text": "Psion's Blade +5, is an enchanted Two Handed Sword +5 that can be found in . It provides protection against confusion and all psionic attacks making it a useful weapon against Illithid and Umber Hulks. Of note, by the time this weapon can be obtained, there may only be two areas where Illithids are present remaining in an unmodded game, those being the &lt;a href=\"Watcher%27s%20Keep%20Illithid%20Encampment\"&gt;Watcher's Keep Illithid Encampment&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Sendai%27s%20Lair%20Mithykyl\"&gt;Sendai's Lair Mithykyl&lt;/a&gt; area.\nAcquisition.\nThe Psion's Blade is hidden in one of the lava-surrounded strongboxes in the outer chambers of &lt;a href=\"Yaga-Shura%27s%20Lair\"&gt;Yaga-Shura's Lair&lt;/a&gt;, hidden in the &lt;a href=\"Marching%20Mountains\"&gt;Marching Mountains&lt;/a&gt;. It can be found in the second tier room on the right-hand side of the map. It is guarded by &lt;a href=\"Flaming%20Skull\"&gt;Flaming Skull&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Fell%20Cat\"&gt;Fell Cat&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Burning%20Man\"&gt;Burning Men&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Salamander\"&gt;Salamander&lt;/a&gt;s."}
